@Mojo(name="dependency-updates-report", requiresDependencyResolution=RUNTIME, threadSafe=true) public class DependencyUpdatesReportMojo extends AbstractDependencyUpdatesReportMojo
Generates a report of available updates for the dependencies of a project.
